    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You begin to generate a surge of twisted medical release chakra designed to tear open wounds and rend the flesh.</p><p>Make a range ninjutsu attack against a creature you can see. On a hit, you deal 3d10 necrotic damage.</p><p>A creature who currently has ranks of bleeding, has one rank of bleeding evolve into one rank of laceration.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3, the damage by 1d10.</p>",
